Introduction

Kim Hyun Jun also known as Tabber, is a South Korean alternative rapper and singer who debuted under You.will.knovv.

On August 13, Tabber released his debut mix tape “Deep End Mixtape”. Before his debut release, he had already collaborated with well-known artists including Punchnello, DEAN, and APRO. After a very successful debut year, Tabber came back in 2021 with the single ‘Electric Animal’ featuring Keyon Christ.

That same year he also participated in the ‘Show Me The Money’ for its 10th season. For this instalment of the popular survival show, he ended in eleventh place and left behind awesome stages. Along with Northfacegawd, EXN, Oygli, and Kwon Ki-Baek, he released the special collaborative album ‘THE: RISE’ for HIPHOPLE.
